prescriptionText: Tab Paracetamol 500mg – 1 tablet every 6 hours for 3 days
Cough syrup 10ml twice a day. Steam inhalation advised.
Loratadine 10mg once daily for 7 days. Apply antihistamine cream.
Azithromycin 250mg – 1 tablet per day for 3 days
Amlodipine 5mg once daily. Reduce salt intake.
Mefenamic Acid 500mg twice daily after meals.
Diclofenac Gel – apply twice a day. Calcium supplement advised.
Eye Drop: Carboxymethylcellulose 1 drop every 4 hrs.
Alprazolam 0.25mg at bedtime, relaxation therapy suggested
Vitamin C and zinc tablets once a day
Cranberry extract capsules twice daily; drink 3L water daily
Tamsulosin 0.4mg once daily after dinner. Hydration recommended
